abstract: He had a pure heart but an empty head.
snippet: He had a pure heart but an empty head.
lead_paragraph: In 2013, I ruled in Floyd vs. City of New York that the tactics underlying the city’s stop-and-frisk program violated the constitutional rights of people of color. While Michael Bloomberg was mayor of New York, black and Latino people were disproportionately stopped, and often frisked, millions of times, peaking at 690,000 in 2011. After my ruling, the number of stops plummeted to 11,000 in 2018. And crime did not rise.

abstract: Former Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid on Wednesday said it was possible the crowded Democratic primary race was headed toward a contentious convention fight and downplayed the political dangers of a scenario many party leaders are dreading.
snippet: Former Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid on Wednesday said it was possible the crowded Democratic primary race was headed toward a contentious convention fight and downplayed the political dangers of a scenario many party leaders are dreading.
lead_paragraph: LAS VEGAS — Former Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid on Wednesday said it was possible the crowded Democratic primary race was headed toward a contentious convention fight and downplayed the political dangers of a scenario many party leaders are dreading.
headline_main: Harry Reid: Brokered Convention 'Not the End of the World'
headline_print_headline: Harry Reid: Brokered Convention 'Not the End of the World'

abstract: Debt-laden HNA Group has restructured jet orders with Europe's Airbus in a compromise deal that includes an order for dozens of A330neo jets, two people familiar with the matter said, amid reports of a wider shake-up at the Chinese conglomerate.
snippet: Debt-laden HNA Group has restructured jet orders with Europe's Airbus in a compromise deal that includes an order for dozens of A330neo jets, two people familiar with the matter said, amid reports of a wider shake-up at the Chinese conglomerate.
lead_paragraph: SHANGHAI — Debt-laden HNA Group has restructured jet orders with Europe's Airbus in a compromise deal that includes an order for dozens of A330neo jets, two people familiar with the matter said, amid reports of a wider shake-up at the Chinese conglomerate.
headline_main: China's HNA Emerges as Recent Buyer of A330neo Jets Amid Revamp: Sources
headline_print_headline: China's HNA Emerges as Recent Buyer of A330neo Jets Amid Revamp: Sources

abstract: When out-of-pocket drug costs rise, patients with common neurological disorders are more likely to forgo their medication, a U.S. study suggests.
snippet: When out-of-pocket drug costs rise, patients with common neurological disorders are more likely to forgo their medication, a U.S. study suggests.
lead_paragraph: (Reuters Health) - When out-of-pocket drug costs rise, patients with common neurological disorders are more likely to forgo their medication, a U.S. study suggests.
headline_main: People Often Skip Neurological Meds When Out-Of-Pocket Costs Rise
headline_print_headline: People Often Skip Neurological Meds When Out-Of-Pocket Costs Rise
